metadata.name: The Chief
metadata.description:
A key to riches, my value is determined by a test of strength.

A grand reward lies ahead, but only for one selected among many champions. The means of choice remain a secret, yet the more fighters in your possession, the higher the odds of ultimate victory.

The journey of my kind doesn't end with a first exchange, it can be passed on, but it holds a greater purpose. Each secondary transfer brings growth and progress to the collective.  In defeat, I may still open doors to abundance for all.
